modName: Dark Brotherhood Tenets - Cool Kid Edition
descriptionHtml: [i]Behold[/i]; a joke mod that more or less still fits seamlessly within the world. If you gave it a short glance, you probably wouldn't even notice anything's different. The text itself was entirely inspired from a poster that briefly shows up in the background in [url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-CNlNYIRw4g]a flash cartoon by OneyNG[/url].  I take no credit for the text itself, only for assembling it in a way that's vaguely lore-friendly. The [url=https://www.filterforge.com/filters/1223-normal.html]paper normal map[/url] is a free to use resource from Filter Forge.
author: Snikkmorder
